==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Thereout
<hw>There*out"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Out
of that or this.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He shall take <qex>thereout</qex> his handful of the flour.</q>
<rj><qau>Lev. ii. 2.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>On the outside; out of doors.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thereto</ent>⟦br⟧
